      <a href="#" class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline mt-2 inline-block">Read more →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md transition-transform transform hover:scale-105">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">
        Debugging: The Art of Talking to Yourself
